column5: Just a few pictures of some fish that were caught over the last few weeks.
Very nice  - that first walleye has just awesome colours
a day on the lake, doesn't matter how many or how big, or the one that broke the line !  it's better than being in the big city ! niice share.
jimmer, looks like you found the secret pike stash on your home lake ?  is that the portable bird i sold ya a while back? still kicking i see!
Yes it is. Had to buy a new transducer for it though. Can you believe the pike that have gotten in there! LOL
